# Simulation Engine

## Governance

Subordinate to `docs/architecture/ai-constitution.md` and `game-domain.mdc`. Simulation is Phase 8 — do not implement without plan and approval per `workflow.mdc`.

| Document | Path |
|----------|------|
| AI Constitution | `docs/architecture/ai-constitution.md` |
| Workflow | `.cursor/rules/workflow.mdc` |
| Universal agent instructions | `AGENTS.md` |
| Project context skill | `.claude/skills/project-context/SKILL.md` |
